                    WAR! Version 1.1 - By Andrew Harrison
                    =====================================
                        2-4 player tank combat game



Requirements
------------

AGA Amiga (A1200, A4000)
2 Joysticks
FAST RAM is strongly recommended as is a 25Mhz or better 68020/030 processor



Controls
--------

Player 1  Joystick in Game Port     Use Down or Button 2 to change weapon
Player 2  Joystick in Mouse Port
Player 3  Keys:
               Ctrl       - Accelerate
               Alt        - Rotate Left
               L Amiga    - Rotate Right
               Blank Key  - Select Weapon
               Z          - Fire Weapon

Player 4  Keys:
               Arrow up      - Accelerate
               Arrow Left    - Rotate Left
               Arrow Right   - Rotate Right
               Numeric pad . - Select Weapon
               Numeric pad 0 - Fire Weapon

Aim of the game
---------------

Simply blast the hell out of your mates tanks with the weapons available to
you. There are two power-ups available in the game. The shield icon restores
a random ammount of your shields energy while the power icon increases your
tanks selected weapon ammo supply. The four green bars next to your tanks
window show how much ammo you have.

Weapons
-------

Weapon 1 - Normal Shot
Weapon 2 - Mines (Lay them in front of the other tanks!)
Weapon 3 - High energy shot (Easier to hit other players)
Weapon 4 - Rebounding bullets (Who will it hit? You!?)

