Future Software
---------------

This is my first game for the Amiga written in Blitz ][
I am in the process of writing a "Lords of Chaos" clone for the Amiga during
1997. A early version of the game will be released before Christmas'97.

"Lords of Chaos" was an old C64 game that made an apperance on the Amiga
years ago. There is already a clone of this classic game out in the public
domain called Fantasy Forces, but I find this to be too limited in terms of
strategy. I hope to improve on both the afore mentioned titles.


If you have any suggestions for this game, please contact me.

